sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant Grid
    participant Cell
    participant Reveal as RevealCtrl
    participant Mimic

    Player->>Grid: Step key (reveal)
    Grid->>Cell: Identify type

    alt First reveal
        Grid->>Grid: Place bombs (exclude first cell + neighbors)
        Grid->>Grid: Compute true numbers
    end

    Cell-->>Reveal: Bomb / Number / Empty

    alt Bomb
        Reveal-->>Player: Game Over
    else Number
        Reveal->>Cell: Show TRUE number
    else Empty (0)
        Reveal->>Grid: Flood reveal nearby cells (bounded)
    end

    Mimic->>Cell: After reveal, change one displayed number